OOC:( Have fun Yanshosh.)

::Battera::

She set the bowl down and looked at Rex. " I'm not the one holding 
the peace conference.  I was sent to talk to the leader about joining 
my fried in the peace talks.  Vulois is the one who is hostig the 
talks.   I was sent to bring back the leader of this Maximal group so 
the table would be complete. I am only an embassador. Nothing more."

She wished she could tell him of the plan in hopes he would trust her 
more.  But it would have been a waste of breath.  She knew he 
wouldn't trust her in a million years, just because she wore a Pred 
symbol.
